    "description": "拿出你的手套和球棒，现在就和史上最强的球员一起上场，尽情游玩《Super Mega Baseball 4》，登上这个传奇球员的舞台。弗拉基米尔·格雷罗、约翰尼·达蒙、奥齐·史密斯和杰森·詹比等 200 多名深受粉丝喜爱的超凡前职业球员已准备好踏入球场，加入备受喜爱的超级联赛全明星阵容。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487210/extras/81610eb72f8a46e7297d1dccd52c3512.poster.avif?t=1748945474\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487210/extras/81610eb72f8a46e7297d1dccd52c3512.webm?t=1748945474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487210/extras/81610eb72f8a46e7297d1dccd52c3512.mp4?t=1748945474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>尽情击球、投球、传球和滑入本垒，体验该系列标志性的街机风格和沉浸式游戏深度。在《Super Mega Baseball 4》中，在全新功能和特许经营及锦标赛†等模式的加持下，棒球变得更加宏大又精良。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487210/extras/f3e912ac3b02133f13e977bd5947c9ad.poster.avif?t=1748945474\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487210/extras/f3e912ac3b02133f13e977bd5947c9ad.webm?t=1748945474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487210/extras/f3e912ac3b02133f13e977bd5947c9ad.mp4?t=1748945474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>此外，该系列的最新作品进行了迄今为止最大规模的呈现方式升级，从动画到角色再到体育场的一切都加上了令人瞠目的新视觉效果，而且从休息区到露天看台都升级了超清晰的音频。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487210/extras/dc25f1bdffd75a7d6d08ec140100384a.poster.avif?t=1748945474\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487210/extras/dc25f1bdffd75a7d6d08ec140100384a.webm?t=1748945474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487210/extras/dc25f1bdffd75a7d6d08ec140100384a.mp4?t=1748945474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>根据社区的反馈，《Super Mega Baseball 4》按照粉丝要求，推出了一系列全新功能，为游戏增添了新的深度，其中包括带有球队默契度的特征系统、洗牌式队员选拔和 6 座全新球场。为扩大玩家群体并提高玩家紧密度，跨平台多人游戏模式已得到了扩展。玩家现可在锦标赛†和在线联赛中进行跨代匹配，从而与更多游戏系统的线上好友一起挥出全垒打。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487210/extras/cfb328b447d7e388dac34716605867b8.poster.avif?t=1748945474\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487210/extras/cfb328b447d7e388dac34716605867b8.webm?t=1748945474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487210/extras/cfb328b447d7e388dac34716605867b8.mp4?t=1748945474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>†锦标赛是一种在线竞技游戏模式，仅支持使用控制器进行游玩；不可使用键盘或鼠标。",
